{% comment %}
  RBP Footer — G1 Global IA Cleanup
  Version: 2.0 | Correct service architecture, no Managed Services
  Architecture: Core Services · On-Demand · Business NBN · Custom Solutions · Membership · Marketplace · Resources · Help
